Date: 1994-04-19

Title: Variational Formulation of Linear Time-Dependent Invariants

Authors: O. Casta\~nos, R. L\'opez-Pe\~na and V.I. Man'ko

Comments: Plain TeX, 9 pages, preprint of Instituto de Ciencias Nucleares, UNAM

Departamento de F\ii sica and Matem\'aticas Aplicadas, M\'exico D. F. ,M\'exico No. 03 (1994)It is shown that linear time-dependent invariants for arbitrarymulti\-dimensional quadratic systems can be obtained from the Lagrangian andHamiltonian formulation procedures by considering a variation of coordinatesand momenta that follows the classical trajectory and defines a noetheriansymmetry transformation.